            <lg xml:id="TK112">
<l>ceppa muṭaiyava ṉākkañ citaiviṉṟi</l>
<l>yeccattiṟ kēmāp puṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wealth of a man of rectitude does not go to waste,</l>
<l>but gives protection to those he leaves behind.</l>
